(13, 'privacy_policy', '{\"privacy_policy\":\"<p><strong>Privacy Policy<br><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Taskify<\\/strong> (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;our,&rdquo; or &ldquo;us&rdquo;) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our platform. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your personal data.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>1. Information We Collect<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We collect the following types of information:<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><strong>1.1 Personal Information<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Name<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Email address<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Contact information<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3><strong>1.2 Non-Personal Information<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Browser type and version<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Device information (e.g., IP address, operating system)<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Usage data (e.g., pages visited, time spent on the platform)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3><strong>1.3 Data You Provide<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Tasks, notes, and other content added to the platform.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>2. How We Use Your Information<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We use your information for the following purposes:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p><strong>To Provide and Maintain the Service<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Create and manage your account.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Facilitate project and task management.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p><strong>To Improve the Service<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Analyze usage patterns to enhance features and functionality.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p><strong>To Communicate With You<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Send updates or notifications.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Respond to inquiries and support requests.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\r\\n<p><strong>For Legal Compliance<\\/strong>:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Fulfill legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our terms.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>3. Sharing Your Information<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others. However, we may share information in the following cases:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><strong>With Service Providers<\\/strong>:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>To support platform operations (e.g., hosting, payment processing).<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>For Legal Reasons<\\/strong>:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>If required by law or to protect our rights, users, or the public.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>4. Data Retention<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We retain your information only as long as necessary to provide the Service and fulfill legal obligations. You may request the deletion of your data at any time.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>5. Data Security<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>6. Your Rights<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>You have the following rights regarding your information:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><strong>Access<\\/strong>: Request access to the personal data we hold about you.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Correction<\\/strong>: Update or correct inaccuracies in your personal data.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Deletion<\\/strong>: Request deletion of your personal data.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\"}', '2024-10-14 17:32:09', '2025-02-04 23:33:58'),
(14, 'about_us', '{\"about_us\":\"<p><strong>About Us<br><br><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Welcome to <strong>Taskify<\\/strong>, your trusted partner in simplifying project management and task organization. We are passionate about empowering individuals and teams to achieve their goals with ease and efficiency.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><strong>Who We Are<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>At Taskify, we believe that productivity thrives when tools are intuitive and streamlined. Founded with a vision to eliminate the chaos of juggling multiple tasks and deadlines, we provide a platform that helps you focus on what matters most&mdash;delivering results.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><strong>What We Do<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Taskify is designed to make managing tasks, projects, invoices, and collaborations seamless. Whether you\'re a solo entrepreneur, a small business, or a growing team, our platform offers the features you need:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><strong>Task Management<\\/strong>: Organize, assign, and track tasks effortlessly.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Invoices and Expenses<\\/strong>: Simplify financial management with detailed tracking and client billing.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Custom Notes<\\/strong>: Add color-coded notes for better prioritization and clarity.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Collaboration Tools<\\/strong>: Stay connected with your team and keep everyone on the same page.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3><strong>Our Mission<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Our mission is to transform the way you manage work by offering a tool that&rsquo;s not just powerful but also incredibly easy to use. We are committed to helping you save time, reduce stress, and achieve more.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><strong>Why Choose Us<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n<li><strong>User-Friendly<\\/strong>: Designed with simplicity and efficiency in mind.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Customizable<\\/strong>: Tailor Taskify to your unique workflow.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Reliable<\\/strong>: A secure and robust platform you can count on.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n<h3><strong>Join Us on the Journey<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We are continually innovating to bring you the best tools and features for your productivity needs. Whether you\'re working on a small project or managing large-scale operations, Taskify is here to support you every step of the way.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3><strong>Get in Touch<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>We&rsquo;d love to hear from you! Share your feedback, suggestions, or simply say hello.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Let&rsquo;s simplify the way you work, together.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\"}', '2024-10-14 17:32:09', '2025-02-04 23:35:07'),
(15, 'terms_conditions', '{\"terms_conditions\":\"<p><strong>Terms and Conditions<br><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><strong>1. Acceptance of Terms<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>By creating an account, accessing, or using Taskify, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, you must discontinue your use of the platform immediately.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>2. Use of the Service<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<h3><strong>2.1 Eligibility<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>You must be at least 18 years old or have the legal capacity to agree to these terms in your jurisdiction.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You are responsible for ensuring the accuracy of the information you provide.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3><strong>2.2 Prohibited Activities<\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>You agree not to:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Use the platform for unlawful or fraudulent purposes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Interfere with or disrupt the platform&rsquo;s functionality.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>3. User Responsibilities<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You are solely responsible for any tasks, projects, or content you add to the platform.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You must comply with all applicable laws and regulations when using the platform.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>4. Service Availability<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We strive to provide uninterrupted access to Taskify. However, we do not guarantee the platform will be available at all times and may suspend access for maintenance or other reasons.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>5. Intellectual Property<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>All content, trademarks, and materials provided on Taskify are the intellectual property of Taskify or its licensors. You may not copy, reproduce, or distribute any content without prior written consent.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>6. Limitation of Liability<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Taskify is not liable for:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the platform.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Loss of data or content due to system errors or unauthorized access.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>7. Termination of Account<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms and Conditions. Upon termination, your access to the platform and its content will be revoked.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>8. Amendments to Terms<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We may update these Terms and Conditions from time to time. Any changes will be effective as of the updated effective date. Continued use of the platform indicates your acceptance of the revised terms.<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<h2><strong>9. Governing Law<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>These Terms and Conditions are governed by the laws of [Insert Jurisdiction]. Any disputes shall be resolved exclusively in the courts of [Insert Jurisdiction].<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\"}', '2024-10-14 17:32:09', '2025-02-04 23:34:39'),
